Glucose: 94 mg/dL
HbA1c: 5.2%
Total Cholesterol: 188 mg/dL
LDL: 112 mg/dL
HDL: 58 mg/dL
Triglycerides: 89 mg/dL
hsCRP: 0.8 mg/L
Vitamin D: 38 ng/mL
TSH: 1.8 mIU/L
Ferritin: 45 ng/mL"></textarea>
        <div class="example-tags">
          <span class="input-label" style="margin:0;line-height:2;">Try an example:</span>
